{"tid":881782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲生日 千語感觸：我錯過你了，你也錯過最好的我了","createTime":"2018-10-29T16:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T05:05:19.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"70ab99b088e2fdc93288d0ea1e4c1451434cc701","tid":881782,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"林峯同吳千語年紀相差14年，今年3月正式宣佈分手。雖然佢哋已各自找到另一半，千語被爆與全國政協施子青長孫施伯雄Brian拍拖，林峯亦戀上大陸o靚模張馨月，但話晒有5年感情，關係又真係好難話斷就斷。<br />\n<br />\n今日係千語BB嘅25歲生日，但就要返橫店拍戲一個月，噚晚千語同助手及大班好朋友一齊慶祝。千語今日都有喺ig story上載開心片段，雖然見唔到男友Brian，但收到五個蛋糕，收穫非常豐富。<br />\n<br />\n阿Sa蔡卓妍都有喺ig祝福壽星女生日快樂，千語即轉載後留言﹕「Xiexie my dearest jiejie(謝謝，我親愛的姐姐)。」咦，乜咁啱嘅，林峯噚日先認咗周勵淇做姐姐，今日又輪到千語叫阿Sa做姐姐，一人嗌一個，誰也搶不了誰的風頭。<br />\n<br />\n近日千語在微博不時會轉帖有關愛情嘅文章，其中一篇講述一對戀人分手，其中一人想重新來過，可惜一切已成定局。「就好像我喜歡你的時候你不喜歡我，你喜歡我的時候我身邊已經有別人了。我對你好的時候你不珍惜，等你回過頭來後悔的時候我已經被別人寵成小公主了。我需要你的時候你都不在，別人已經出現在我的生活裏替代你了。<br />\n<br />\n「你說不如我們重新來過，我說來不及了，真的來不及了。&hellip;&hellip;我錯過你了，你也錯過最好的我了。」由於故事情節似曾相識，有網民就大膽猜測﹕「千語BB對林峯的真情流露」。"},{"pid":"7f2acf854f66e10d5f3833ad00d45759f26918fa","tid":881782,"uid":10277,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167e00bf9d276ccacde6dbd41d04be8c66a1e0b5","tid":881782,"uid":36296,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187495665885856732cc12030c41060ebf7f8a40","tid":881782,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:49:05.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"0b862827ce44e2767e36e34e346e4d67c8d9fdce","tid":881782,"uid":139720,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"乜撚野xie jie呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f84c0dfa1a785a12a627d7b6b6c6bb2c200ace","tid":881782,"uid":56999,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"你也錯過最好的我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊個處"},{"pid":"6ead84a7a87efdc5cde607c656af813ac854568a","tid":881782,"uid":147522,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"林峯值得一個更好既女人"},{"pid":"c1ea081593ff3f97e12cb18c0a693c56c79e2436","tid":881782,"uid":2033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦臭雞"},{"pid":"cf9c1d8918d56625399f1ace5697a37d2277e39a","tid":881782,"uid":88503,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"林峯仲唔夠寵佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要打跛對腳八人大轎抬去歐洲旅行先叫寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208c983d85aa45b8f7504d349c6923af7c504377","tid":881782,"uid":32114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f84c0dfa1a785a12a627d7b6b6c6bb2c200ace","tid":881782,"uid":56999,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"你也錯過最好的我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪講緊個處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T20:07:26.000Z","msg":"林峯都要執黃百嗚二攤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70a0837030cd4d2c8e966934bc5cce46522279c","tid":881782,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"Xiexie my dearest jieji<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飛得好"},{"pid":"90e37f2b5ce7daa9d53ef14055cfa7de66157e68","tid":881782,"uid":4210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"原來佢先25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid